c: 4
v: 83
t: "Bwebajjirwa e kigambo e kyemirembe oba e kyentiisa bakiraalaasa, so singa bakizza eri omubaka oba abo abakwatibwako ensonga mu bo, bandikitegedde abo abalina obusobozi bwokusengejja amakulu gaayo, singa tebyali birungi Katonda byabawa n’okusaasira kwe mwandigoberedde Sitane mpozzi abatono mu mmwe"